data.description: Wow. The views from the back porch of this home are really stunning. It feels like your own little world, looking out onto the beautiful pines on this one acre lot. But, before you get there, you will enter the house and see the open floor plan of the kitchen, dining area, living room with wood burning stove and access to the 2 car garage. Off the living area, there is a primary suite with walk in closet and full bath, 2 additional bedrooms, full bath and laundry room. The yard is fully fenced with a storage shed for landscape supplies. This homes was built with many "green" features such as choice of wood, water filtration system and even eco friendly paint. High end finishes include custom bathroom sinks, mirrors and stainless steel appliances. The HVAC was replaced in 2021 and stainless steel appliances were replaced in 2021.
